  <entry>
    <title>用户配置脚本文件.netrc</title>
    <link href="http://kekxv.github.io/2021/08/07/%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6.netrc/"/>
    <id>http://kekxv.github.io/2021/08/07/%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6.netrc/</id>
    <published>2021-08-07T07:10:21.596Z</published>
    <updated>2021-08-07T07:10:21.596Z</updated>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;The .netrc file contains login and initialization information used by the auto-login process. It generally resides in the user’s home directory, but a location outside of the home directory can be set using the environment variable NETRC. Both locations are overridden by the command line option -N. The selected file must be a regular file, or access will be denied.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;用于配置网络登录帐号信息的 &lt;code&gt;~/.netrc&lt;/code&gt; 文件,保存用户名密码，减少输用户名密码。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;文件 &lt;code&gt;~/.netrc&lt;/code&gt; 用于设置自动登录时所需要的帐号信息。&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
    
